channel.title: I can't put 669/704 online! Help!
channel.description:
Hey...i got another problem, this time...with putting the server online. Here is what I did:
1. I portforwarded my router to 43594, checked it out and it works.
2. After that, I made sure that I had my no-ip up and running. It also worked.
3. I used eclipse to edit the ip located in the client's loader.java file.
4. I compiled.
5. I tested it out on myself, and its stuck on 1% loading....
6. I gave the client with my no-ip to my friend, and the same result; 1% loading...... and nothing happens.
Result: I dont know what the problem is...i worked with it in localhost and it worked well, my friend claims that it's the problem with the client, or maybe I'm changing the ip in the wrong section....(but many people told me it's loader.java)
Please help me! Thank you.
